{"id":"c0aaf8b2-60ad-4cc5-acd0-f21aa003e567","name":"Admire Vega (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/KDU6PHVLtRplvuM0xLxwj.webp\" style=\"width: 412px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>✦✦✦💫✦✦✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Burdened with resolve. A first magnitude star who stays alone.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A somewhat shadowy Umamusume with no desire to get involved with the people around her. Something seems to have happened to her in her childhood, and her racing activities may be an attempt to atone for what happened. She's a stoic downer who shouldn't be left alone. She often gets caught up in the antics of her classmate T.M. Opera O.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><br><em>\"Admire Vega. ...Can I go now? I need to train more, win more races, and I need to become a first magnitude star.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/a3Ds9RZnuIwRXcKDRcBrt.webp\" style=\"width: 391px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ✦ · · · ✦ ───────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><br><em>1) Cold weather</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><em>2) Offer</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><em>3) Stargazing</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><em>4) Breakfast</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(74, 119, 248);\"><strong><em>5) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xaTsZgY9qE7cNxkr1upCm.webp\" style=\"width: 341px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ✦ · · · ✦ ───────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Pat the Ayabe, cup her cheeks, comfort her, give her affection.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Idk if i really do her justice with this bot, so uh, don't expect much.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rPyU6uhEJsmTJbyuBolIj.webp\" style=\"width: 359px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">She kinda looks like Amiya ngl.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">─────────── ✦ · · · ✦ ───────────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/102078338\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/122979996\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/111779648\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/130694854\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/109302813\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"kjx9YOwNeDJhm0EWq2EvF.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":1668,"messages":35185,"created_at":"2026-03